des: The website StockCalc.com calculates fundamental valuation for 8000 stocks, 800 ETFs, and 150 industries each night. With this Alexa skill you can ask StockCalc for the fundamental valuation for any company trading on the major North American markets (NYS, NAS, ASE, TSE, TSX).
